then of course uh to try and do some some sitting it doesn't matter how long you know it doesn't matter how long five minutes ten minutes uh before you eat i mean you know doing it after you eat is miserable you just fall asleep so it's okay so and then and then you've got the evening you see uh you know with more energy so um these are just sort of basic um

97
00:14:03,022 --> 00:14:08,208
reminders, you know, on how to sort of go through the day gently, at ease.

98
